    "body": "I agree that improved navigation is essential. I spend most of my time in IPython just looking for things. I strongly suggest an interface similar to Sublime Text's Cmd+P \"Goto Anything\" dialog. Keyboard shortcuts are infinitely faster than buttons and I think that it's fair to say that \"Goto Anything\" is one of Sublime's keys to success.\n"
